description:
Stagecoach Santa (2014) | Trailer | Ron Randolph | Deirdre Harmon | Byron Lambie | Cynthia Speakman

After the loss of the family farm, the Thompsons head west for a fresh start. Johns struggle to provide for his family is bolstered by the childlike faith of his young son who, despite his new environment, inspires everyone he meets to consider the true meaning of Christmas. After a mysterious stagecoach rider visits in the dark hours of Christmas Eve, even John must believe that his troubles are temporary, and miracles do happen on Christmas. 

Director: Gary Tomsic
Starring: Ron Randolph, Deirdre Harmon, Byron Lambie, Cynthia Speakman, Jon Pauling
Available Fall 2014 from Vision Video
